## Testing Complex Logic

```ruby
test "calculates discount based on user tier" do
  gold_user = users(:gold)
  silver_user = users(:silver)
  
  assert_equal 0.20, gold_user.discount_rate
  assert_equal 0.15, silver_user.discount_rate
end

test "applies tiered pricing correctly" do
  product = products(:one)
  
  assert_equal 100, product.price_for_quantity(1)
  assert_equal 90, product.price_for_quantity(10)
  assert_equal 80, product.price_for_quantity(100)
end
```

